{"tid":1469740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不如整個 由運動開始到依家哩一刻發生過既事 既資料整合 比香港人睇？","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:56:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T04:28:44.000Z","uid":48125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1458cbe1098be11161b234b791a122c716c69307","tid":1469740,"uid":48125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:56:03.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">香港人有善忘既個性，所以更加要keep住提醒初心<br />\n可以係機場整條pathway／搵個area，remind六個烈士，71衝入立法會，721警黑合作，所有所有<br />\n所有手足一齊做，都可以相對避免鬼搞事。<br />\n亦都可以代入連儂效果，若果佢地每日清，我地就每日做。<br />\n同時媒體黎既時候都可以將所有陋行一次過爆比佢地知。<br />\n大家覺得點？<br />\n做到 解釋＋道歉＋反擊＋提升形象＋將消息散播出去</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">快啲一齊討論！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"f8d00ec55ba5323f56520732c55b4bd668d37fdb","tid":1469740,"uid":48125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:56:28.000Z","msg":"721，811"},{"pid":"6e60ab2e31be6f35c746630713d456ed7abd3fa2","tid":1469740,"uid":48125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:56:38.000Z","msg":"721，811"},{"pid":"342242e5344d7678ced177ac7c1e78cafbd0f005","tid":1469740,"uid":48125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:56:55.000Z","msg":"721，811"},{"pid":"bf83cf1b95ab38a8b5b64de780385a0308e73749","tid":1469740,"uid":48125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:57:05.000Z","msg":"721，811"},{"pid":"171310042df803ffc0b389133daf5deac77ba729","tid":1469740,"uid":48125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:57:21.000Z","msg":"721，811"},{"pid":"0020ba95f078f1de86d9f0bbc1e91186d0d768c9","tid":1469740,"uid":48125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:57:40.000Z","msg":"721，811"},{"pid":"dc016aba9d30108bb919257d7c59d0c0d838471a","tid":1469740,"uid":48125,"like":0,"dis